From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Date: Mon, 16 Feb 2026 17:48:25 +1100
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: cix: Add Sky1 miscellaneous peripheral drivers

Add GPT timer, fan controller (hwmon), GPIO cadence edge IRQ
and PM/wake/ACPI support, RTC wake-up, PWM controller, watchdog,
DMA-350 ACPI fix, CMA heap, SPI/I2C/I3C cadence fixes, backlight,
bluetooth crash fix, pstore ACPI, SMMUv3 ATS override, SPE fix,
and kernel DMA coherent helper.
